  - Verify `dp_client.invoke()` called with correct params\n164:   - Verify parsed JSON returned\n165:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n166:   - Verify: Delegation works\n167: \n168: - [ ] **T4.9** Test `AgentRuntimeClient.invoke()` without session\n169:   - Verify `ValueError` raised when session_id is None\n170:   - Verify error message clear\n171:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n172:   - Verify: Protection works\n173: \n174: - [ ] **T4.10** Test `AgentRuntimeClient.invoke()` with timeout override\n175:   - Verify timeout param passed to dp_client\n176:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n177:   - Verify: Timeout override works\n178: \n179: - [ ] **T4.11** Test `AgentRuntimeClient.close()`\n180:   - Verify `dp_client.close()` called\n181:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n182:   - Verify: Cleanup delegated\n183: \n184: - [ ] **T4.12** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.__init__()` base URL computation\n185:   - Verify URL format: `{router_url}/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/`\n186:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n187:   - Verify: URL computed correctly\n188: \n189: - [ ] **T4.13** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.SESSION_HEADER` constant\n190:   - Verify equals `\"x-agentcube-session-id\"` (lowercase)\n191:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n192:   - Verify: Constant correct\n193: \n194: - [ ] **T4.14** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.bootstrap_session_id()` success\n195:   - Mock GET response with session header\n196:   - Verify header value returned\n197:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n198:   - Verify: Session ID extracted\n199: \n200: - [ ] **T4.15** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.bootstrap_session_id()` missing header\n201:   - Mock GET response without session header\n202:   - Verify `ValueError` raised with clear message\n203:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n204:   - Verify: Error handling\n205: \n206: - [ ] **T4.16** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.bootstrap_session_id()` request\n207:   - Verify GET to base_url with timeout tuple\n208:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n209:   - Verify: Request correct\n210: \n211: - [ ] **T4.17** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.invoke()` POST request\n212:   - Verify POST to base_url with JSON body\n213:   - Verify session header set\n214:   - Verify Content-Type header set\n215:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n216:   - Verify: Request correct\n217: \n218: - [ ] **T4.18** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.invoke()` timeout handling\n219:   - Test default timeout from instance\n220:   - Test timeout override\n221:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n222:   - Verify: Timeout applied correctly\n223: \n224: - [ ] **T4.19** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.invoke()` response\n225:   - Verify `requests.Response` returned\n226:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n227:   - Verify: Response returned\n228: \n229: - [ ] **T4.20** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.close()`\n230:   - Verify `session.close()` called\n231:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n232:   - Verify: HTTP session closed\n233: \n234: ---\n235: \n236: ## Phase 5: Integration Tests\n237: \n238: - [ ] **T5.1** Create integration test fixture\n239:   - Check for `ROUTER_URL` env var\n240:   - Create `AgentRuntimeClient` instance\n241:   - Cleanup on teardown\n242:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/integration/test_agent_runtime.py`\n243:   - Verify: Tests skip if env var missing\n244: \n245: - [ ] **T5.2** Test `AgentRuntimeClient` bootstrap\n246:   - Create client without session_id\n247:   - Verify session_id bootstrapped\n248:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/integration/test_agent_runtime.py`\n249: