y: No mypy errors\n303: \n304: - [ ] **T6.7** Run ruff/flake8 linting\n305:   - Command: `ruff check sdk-python/agentcube/`\n306:   - Fix all lint errors\n307:   - Verify: No lint errors\n308: \n309: - [ ] **T6.8** Run pytest with coverage\n310:   - Command: `pytest --cov=agentcube sdk-python/tests/`\n311:   - Verify coverage >= 80%\n312:   - Verify: All methods tested\n313: \n314: ---\n315: \n316: ## Phase 7: Examples & Documentation\n317: \n318: - [ ] **T7.1** Create `examples/agent_runtime_basic.py`\n319:   - Show `AgentRuntimeClient` with `with` statement\n320:   - Demonstrate `invoke()`\n321:   - Show context manager cleanup\n322:   - File: `sdk-python/examples/agent_runtime_basic.py`\n323:   - Verify: Example is runnable\n324: \n325: - [ ] **T7.2** Create `examples/agent_runtime_explicit_session.py`\n326:   - Show providing explicit `session_id`\n327:   - Demonstrate session reuse\n328:   - File: `sdk-python/examples/agent_runtime_explicit_session.py`\n329:   - Verify: Example is runnable\n330: \n331: - [ ] **T7.3** Update `README.md`\n332:   - Add `AgentRuntimeClient` section\n333:   - Installation instructions\n334:   - Quick start examples\n335:   - API overview\n336:   - Environment variables\n337:   - File: `sdk-python/README.md`\n338:   - Verify: Clear documentation\n339: \n340: ---\n341: \n342: ## Acceptance Criteria\n343: \n344: 1. ✅ `AgentRuntimeClient` bootstraps session_id via GET invocation endpoint when not provided\n345: 2. ✅ `AgentRuntimeClient` reuses provided session_id without bootstrap\n346: 3. ✅ Router URL resolves from arg → `ROUTER_URL` env → `ValueError`\n347: 4. ✅ Context manager `__exit__` calls `close()`, cleans up HTTP session\n348: 5. ✅ `invoke()` raises `ValueError` if session_id not initialized\n349: 6. ✅ `invoke()` returns parsed JSON from response\n350: 7. ✅ Per-call timeout override works in `invoke(timeout=60)`\n351: 8. ✅ Timeout defaults: read=120s, connect=5.0s\n352: 9. ✅ Session header uses lowercase `x-agentcube-session-id`\n353: 10. ✅ Base URL computed: `{router_url}/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/`\n354: 11. ✅ HTTP session with connection pooling (10/10)\n355: 12. ✅ `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.bootstrap_session_id()` raises `ValueError` on missing header\n356: 13. ✅ Package installs via `pip install .`\n357: 14. ✅ Imports work: `from agentcube import AgentRuntimeClient`\n358: 15. ✅ Unit tests cover all clients and error cases (>= 80% coverage)\n359: 16. ✅ Integration tests pass in live environment\n360: 17. ✅ Type hints pass mypy validation\n361: 18. ✅ Code passes ruff/flake8 linting\n362: 19. ✅ Examples provided and runnable\n363: 20. ✅ README documents installation and usage\n364: \n365: ---\n366: \n367: **Notes:**\n368: - Stage ST-3: Design completed, implementation pending\n369: - Session header naming: uses lowercase `x-agentcube-session-id` throughout\n370: - Timeout handling: no buffer needed (unlike CodeInterpreterClient execute_command)\n371: - Session bootstrap: happens in `__init__` if session_id not provided\n372: - No control plane involvement (unlike CodeInterpreterClient)\n373: - Router URL required: no fallback to default, must be provided or in env\n\n(End of file - total 373 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-028 — SDK AgentRuntimeClient Tasks\n\n**Module:** sdk-python  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Package Structure & Exports\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Update `agentcube/__init__.py`\n  - Import `AgentRuntimeClient` from `agent_runtime`\n  - Update `__all__` to include `\"AgentRuntimeClient\"`\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/__init__.py`\n  - Verify: `from agentcube import AgentRuntimeClient` works\n\n- [ ] **T1.2** Update `agentcube/clients/__init__.py`\n  - Import `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` from `agent_runtime_data_plane`\n  - Add to `__all__` list","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20